Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.44,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:27.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}I'm proud of myself and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:30.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}We must be the change we wish to see...
